FBIS3-18207 "drweu040aa_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 March 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Canada: NATO Attacks `Authorized' LD2802220894 Montreal Radio Canada International in English 2130 GMT 28 Feb 94 LD2802220894 Montreal Radio Canada International Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Canada supports NATO's decision to shoot down four Bosnian Serb planes today. Foreign affairs spokesman (Denis Boulet) says the NATO attacks were authorized by United Nations Security Council resolutions. Mr. (Boulet) says Canada has received no reports of reprisals against peacekeeping troops in Bosnia, including more than 800 Canadian soldiers. [passage omitted]
